summary: You want to look like a cute idol girl. Well here is the perfect non-immersive female skin!
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://oi66.tinypic.com/1jxges.jpg[/img]
[img]https://m-master.000webhostapp.com/2.png[/img]


[center]This mod replaces the face and body textures for all females with realistic yet flawless skin to make your Character look like a idol girl .
I have included old Babydoll normal maps if you want your character to look younger. The lips are made to look realistic.

The body skin is 4k and the rest is 2k. For 2k option only , please install main and then the 2k texture replacer.

Good to know, may look off on ECE but works best on Racemenu.

[color=#ead1dc][size=3][b][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/84687/?]You can find old version here

[/url][/b][/size][/color]

FAQ:[/color][/b][/size][size=5][b]
[/b][/size]
[b]Q:I have a neckseam:[/b]
A: Be sure to uninstall your previous skin mod, or they may "clash".
Also meshes that replaces feet or hands may sometimes "distort" certain parts of the skin.

[b]Q: Will you make a Potato patch?[/b]
A: Yes, soon.

[b]Q: Can you share uncompressed version of the skin?
[/b]No I will not.

[b]Q: Patch to SSE?[/b]
A: No, if you want to do it and credit me, go ahead.
[b]
Q: Your skin looks awful! Why is the nose red?[/b]
A: Because it is suppose to look cute, if you donÂ´t like it. Then please look for another skin mod.

[b]
[b]Q: Your skin is to pale![/b]
[/b]A: Try picking a darker skin color then? Most if not all skins are pale.[b][/b]

[b]Q: May I add your skin to a Russian / Japanese website?[/b]
No, you may translate my mod.

[b]Q: Can I publish this on Xbone? Make it a paid mod?[/b]
No, I do not allow it.

[b]Q: My skin looks nothing like in your pictures:[/b]
A: Different enbs will give different result. Vanilla light may come off as shiny.
[b]
Q: The eyes on the High elf, where can I get it?[/b]
A: It is a eye mod I am working on, stay tuned.


[color=#a2c4c9][b]All complains will be simply deleted, criticism is always wanted.
And thank you for downloading
